:

1. *Bilo* je mnogo posla. (There was a lot of work.)
2. Čuo sam da *bilo* je lepih mesta u prirodi. (I heard there were beautiful places in nature.)
3. *Bili* su srećni da se vide. (They were happy to see each other.)
4. Da li *bilo* je još kruha? (Was there any more bread?)
5. *Budući* da je večeras praznik, biće mnogo ljudi. (Since it's a holiday tonight, there will be a lot of people.)